[
    {
        "text": "- In April 1995, a truck\nbomb ripped apart a building",
        "start": 0.73,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "in downtown Oklahoma City.",
        "start": 4.15,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "In August 2015, a series\nof explosions shook",
        "start": 6.76,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": "the port of Tianjin and northern China.",
        "start": 10.09,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "And in August 2020, a\nwarehouse fire set off",
        "start": 13.23,
        "duration": 3.07
    },
    {
        "text": "a blast in Beirut so powerful",
        "start": 16.3,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "that neighboring countries could feel it.",
        "start": 18.77,
        "duration": 2.093
    },
    {
        "text": "These were all caused by the\ncompound ammonium nitrate,",
        "start": 22.6,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "which over the last\ncentury has been involved",
        "start": 25.6,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "in at least 30 disasters\nand terrorist attacks.",
        "start": 27.68,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "But what is ammonium nitrate?",
        "start": 30.89,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, it's used in all kinds of things",
        "start": 33.21,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "from making antibiotics\nto instant cold packs.",
        "start": 35.01,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's a key ingredient in fertilizer.",
        "start": 38.55,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "You might be wondering,",
        "start": 41.03,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Why are we using something that has",
        "start": 42.27,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "the potential to be so\ndeadly to grow food?",
        "start": 43.96,
        "duration": 3.527
    },
    {
        "text": "(music chime)",
        "start": 47.487,
        "duration": 3.263
    },
    {
        "text": "I like to think of ammonium nitrate as",
        "start": 50.75,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "a Jekyll and Hyde chemical.",
        "start": 52.41,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "When it's stored properly,",
        "start": 54.28,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "it's the mild mannered Dr. Jekyll.",
        "start": 55.79,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Plants love it",
        "start": 58.17,
        "duration": 1.49
    },
    {
        "text": "because it supplies them with nitrogen",
        "start": 59.66,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "which they need to grow.",
        "start": 61.1,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "And although our atmosphere\nis mostly nitrogen,",
        "start": 62.8,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "plants can't actually use it in that form,",
        "start": 65.05,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "but they can use it in\nthe form of nitrate.",
        "start": 67.65,
        "duration": 3.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Under the wrong conditions,",
        "start": 71.05,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "ammonium nitrate can turn into",
        "start": 72.34,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Dr. Jekyll's evil alter ego,",
        "start": 74.1,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "Mr. Hyde.",
        "start": 76.89,
        "duration": 0.97
    },
    {
        "text": "- [MAN] Window",
        "start": 77.86,
        "duration": 0.862
    },
    {
        "text": "- [BOY] Are you serious?",
        "start": 78.722,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "- [MAN] Yeah.\n(explosion)",
        "start": 79.555,
        "duration": 1.655
    },
    {
        "text": "So what makes this normally\nharmless compound turn deadly?",
        "start": 81.21,
        "duration": 4.41
    },
    {
        "text": "First, you need a lot of it.",
        "start": 85.62,
        "duration": 1.91
    },
    {
        "text": "There's this thing\ncalled critical diameter,",
        "start": 87.53,
        "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
        "text": "which is essentially\nthe amount of a compound",
        "start": 90.15,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "you would need for it to detonate.",
        "start": 92.33,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "Ammonium nitrate is\ncritical diameter is huge,",
        "start": 94.4,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "about 100 times bigger than TNTs.",
        "start": 97.42,
        "duration": 3.297
    },
    {
        "text": "- And it's quite inert by itself.",
        "start": 100.717,
        "duration": 3.063
    },
    {
        "text": "But sometimes if there's a fire",
        "start": 103.78,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "quite near the ammonium nitrate,",
        "start": 107.03,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "and ammonium nitrate is in a huge pile,",
        "start": 109.78,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "ammonium nitrate can catch on fire.",
        "start": 113.71,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "- Once ammonium nitrate\nreaches 210 degrees Celsius,",
        "start": 116.53,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "it starts to melt,",
        "start": 119.81,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "quickly producing a bunch of gases,",
        "start": 121.1,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "mainly nitrous oxide,",
        "start": 123.03,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "water vapor and nitrogen gas.",
        "start": 124.67,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "If those gases can't escape,",
        "start": 127.1,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "temperatures go up",
        "start": 128.63,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "and the reaction gets faster and faster.",
        "start": 129.65,
        "duration": 2.923
    },
    {
        "text": "Now this on its own could\nlead to an explosion.",
        "start": 133.48,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "In the case of a Beirut,",
        "start": 136.48,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "6 million pounds of ammonium nitrate",
        "start": 138.12,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "had been improperly stored in a warehouse,",
        "start": 140.9,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "sitting around and soaking up moisture",
        "start": 143.49,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "for nearly seven years.",
        "start": 145.39,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "- And particularly though\nnitrate has been a bit wet,",
        "start": 147.69,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "it becomes very hard like cement,",
        "start": 150.51,
        "duration": 2.17
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not fluffy powder anymore",
        "start": 152.68,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "- So out of fire,",
        "start": 154.74,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "and that hardened ammonium nitrate starts",
        "start": 156.36,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "to heat up and melts.",
        "start": 158.5,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "- And then the pressure starts to increase",
        "start": 160.2,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "where the gases can't escape.",
        "start": 162.03,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "- The burn rate or the speed\nat which ammonium nitrate",
        "start": 163.81,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "is burning starts to pick up.",
        "start": 166.42,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "When the burn rate is",
        "start": 168.5,
        "duration": 0.92
    },
    {
        "text": "slower than the speed of sound,",
        "start": 169.42,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "that's deflagration,",
        "start": 171.3,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "but when it becomes faster\nthan the speed of sound,",
        "start": 173.34,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "that causes a shockwave through",
        "start": 176.21,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "the ammonium nitrate which detonates it.",
        "start": 178.34,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "But ammonium nitrate doesn't",
        "start": 181.28,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "need to be in a compressed\nform to create a disaster.",
        "start": 183.21,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "At the port of Tianjin,",
        "start": 186.87,
        "duration": 1.123
    },
    {
        "text": "1.7 million pounds of ammonium\nnitrate was being stored in",
        "start": 187.993,
        "duration": 4.377
    },
    {
        "text": "a warehouse near a place\nwhere nitrocellulose",
        "start": 192.37,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "was also being stored.",
        "start": 194.53,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Unlike ammonium nitrate,",
        "start": 195.93,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "nitrocellulose is highly flammable.",
        "start": 197.37,
        "duration": 2.98
    },
    {
        "text": "The nitrocellulose caught fire,",
        "start": 200.35,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "spreading to the stored ammonium nitrate,",
        "start": 202.11,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "causing it to detonate.",
        "start": 203.98,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Tianjin and Beirut were some of",
        "start": 206.26,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "the deadliest accidental\nammonium nitrate disasters over",
        "start": 207.76,
        "duration": 3.35
    },
    {
        "text": "the last century.",
        "start": 211.11,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "But terrorists have also\nweaponized the chemical.",
        "start": 212.2,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Like in the 1995 Oklahoma City bombing,",
        "start": 215.02,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "where terrorist detonated a truck",
        "start": 217.86,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "loaded with 5,000 pounds of\nammonium nitrate fertilizer,",
        "start": 219.54,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "killing 168 people.",
        "start": 223.14,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "When I see a large explosion on the news,",
        "start": 226.06,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "my first instinct is to ask,",
        "start": 228.03,
        "duration": 2.207
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Was that an accident?",
        "start": 230.237,
        "duration": 1.883
    },
    {
        "text": "Or was it planned?\"",
        "start": 232.12,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "- If its a terrorist attack,",
        "start": 233.96,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "you wouldn't have a fire,",
        "start": 235.41,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "it will happen very quickly.",
        "start": 236.67,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "You wouldn't have time\nfor people to video it,",
        "start": 237.9,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "it'll be done",
        "start": 240.12,
        "duration": 1.21
    },
    {
        "text": "within minutes.",
        "start": 241.33,
        "duration": 0.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Because what they're doing,",
        "start": 242.28,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "they have the explosive,",
        "start": 243.53,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "they will detonate it,",
        "start": 244.68,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "cause a blast do the\nutmost damage they can",
        "start": 246.47,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "and that's it.",
        "start": 249.69,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "- Because of its prevalence\nand terrorist attacks,",
        "start": 251.2,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Some countries have\noutlawed ammonium nitrate.",
        "start": 253.33,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "In one instance in 2011,",
        "start": 256.49,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "the US Army detonated about 2,000 pounds",
        "start": 258.35,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "of ammonium nitrate fertilizer",
        "start": 261.34,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "that it collected in Afghanistan.",
        "start": 262.88,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "It was done very far away from homes",
        "start": 264.98,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "or people so the resulting shockwave",
        "start": 267.29,
        "duration": 2.21
    },
    {
        "text": "wouldn't cause damage or injury.",
        "start": 269.5,
        "duration": 1.843
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes the shockwave is more deadly",
        "start": 274.51,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "than the explosion itself.",
        "start": 276.55,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "- A shockwave is compressing",
        "start": 278.61,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "the air going through the atmosphere,",
        "start": 281.06,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "and at the tip of the shockwave,",
        "start": 283.71,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "the temperatures are three\nto 4,000 degrees centigrade",
        "start": 285.4,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "and the speed of the\nshockwave is supersonic.",
        "start": 289.02,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "So as a shock waves going\nthrough the atmosphere as it hits",
        "start": 291.95,
        "duration": 3.94
    },
    {
        "text": "windows of course it shatters them because",
        "start": 295.89,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "it pushes them out.",
        "start": 298.26,
        "duration": 1.39
    },
    {
        "text": "As it hits people,",
        "start": 299.65,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "it'll break our bones",
        "start": 301.03,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "because they're brittle,",
        "start": 302.26,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "but the rest of it will go through",
        "start": 303.22,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "but it'll burn us because it's very hot.",
        "start": 304.77,
        "duration": 2.85
    },
    {
        "text": "It'll flip over cars,",
        "start": 307.62,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "it will flip over ships.",
        "start": 309.32,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "It'll break anything brittle.",
        "start": 311.09,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "it will shatter anything brittle as",
        "start": 312.88,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "it goes through the atmosphere.",
        "start": 315.52,
        "duration": 1.49
    },
    {
        "text": "- So if you find yourself in a place",
        "start": 317.01,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "where you see a massive fire burning,",
        "start": 318.43,
        "duration": 2.41
    },
    {
        "text": "get as far away from it as possible",
        "start": 320.84,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "and away from any windows because",
        "start": 322.58,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "you don't know what's burning.",
        "start": 324.3,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "So if it detonates,",
        "start": 326.12,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "the shockwave that follows\ncould be devastating.",
        "start": 328.09,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, all of this is scary.",
        "start": 330.98,
        "duration": 2.111
    },
    {
        "text": "But Dr. Akhavan made it clear that",
        "start": 333.091,
        "duration": 2.719
    },
    {
        "text": "we should not be freaked\nout about ammonium nitrate.",
        "start": 335.81,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "- Because people worry now,",
        "start": 338.6,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "so they shouldn't be worried\nabout ammonium nitrate.",
        "start": 340.14,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "It is safe to use.",
        "start": 342.98,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Its nothing more.",
        "start": 345.38,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "It's not classed as an explosive.",
        "start": 346.213,
        "duration": 1.987
    },
    {
        "text": "So very rarely does it go up.",
        "start": 348.2,
        "duration": 3.29
    },
    {
        "text": "It's only when it's old,",
        "start": 351.49,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "and there's a fire next door",
        "start": 353.92,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "and also stored in huge quantities.",
        "start": 356.02,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Otherwise it's fine.",
        "start": 358.08,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "- So having a bag of\nammonium nitrate fertilizer",
        "start": 359.6,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "in your garage is not cause for concern.",
        "start": 362.35,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "So keep on using it,",
        "start": 365.45,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "your tomatoes will probably thank you.",
        "start": 367.23,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Happy gardening.",
        "start": 369.24,
        "duration": 1.134
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat outro music)",
        "start": 370.374,
        "duration": 3.083
    }
]